Chinese-Government Backed Debt Is ‘Staggering,’ Chanos Says

-- B y   S t e v e n   C r a b i l l
-- 
2011-09-20T19:46:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/chinese-government-backed-debt-is-staggering-chanos-says.html
Jim Chanos , founder of Kynikos
Associates Ltd. hedge fund, said the amount of Chinese-backed
debt in state-owned industries and local governments is
“staggering.”  Chanos, speaking today in an interview on Bloomberg
Television’s “Street Smart,” said his New York-based hedge
fund has shorted Chinese banks and property developers.  To contact the reporter on this story:
